for installing spdlog X.X.X:
Download spdlog release vX.X.X (get the latest) from the github: https://github.com/gabime/spdlog/releases
sftp it to your VM
untar it -> tar -xzf spdlog....tar.gz
cd into it -> cd spdlog...X.X.X
mkdir build && cd build
sudo cmake3 -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release --build .. --target install

NOTE: if you don't have cmake3 then do: sudo yum install -y cmake3